{{Otheruses|Coffee}}
{{Quote|I have been waiting 1 week, 3 days and 5 hours for you to bring me my coffee. I condemn you to death!|[[Rel Rogock]]|<ref name="SWG:OoMM">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=general|Out of My Mine|Lok}}</ref>}}
'''Coffee''' was a non-[[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage that was most often served extremely hot and made from a specific type of bean.

[[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] owned [[Farm/Legends|farms]] on various [[Planet/Legends|planets]] that provided the beans to produce high quality coffee and [[vine-coffee]], solely for the use of his court.

Coffee could be prepared and dispensed from a [[Coffee machine/Legends|coffee machine]], and was usually served in a coffee cup.

==Behind the scenes==
{{Noncanonstart|legends=1}}
During a discussion of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]] with the [[Palpatine/Legends|Emperor]], [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]], [[Wilhuff Tarkin/Legends|Wilhuff Tarkin]] and other high-ranking [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] personnel, Wilhuff Tarkin drank some.
{{Noncanonend}}

